posting_body: ['***2 BEDROOM RENT SPECIAL: ONE MONTH FREE!', '*** CALL TODAY FOR MORE DETAILS', '800 Sq.', 'Ft.', '$40 Application Fee/ Adult', '$500 Deposit', 'Why Choose Us?', 'We are a one-stop-shop!', 'We have multiple properties in prime Metro locations - so you can work with one Leasing Agent and still choose from multiple options, prices and properties.', 'Bonus ~ We have Month to Month Rental Agreements at no up-charge!', 'We are locally owned and operated and have been in business in the Metro for 40 years.', 'These properties are convenient for commuters who want to be near Downtown Minneapolis and the University of Minnesota.', 'MANAGEMENT PAYS ALL UTILITIES, Except Electric.', '24 HOUR MAINTENANCE', 'AMAZING OFFICE STAFF', 'Cats are accepted.', '$250 non-refundable pet fee per cat and $30/month pet rent per cat.', 'Ask for full guidelines on Pet Policy.', 'Call or email us today to schedule a showing or for more information!', 'Call now', 'show contact info', 'Or, visit our website for more pics at <URL>', "*Don't Wait ~ Prices and availability are subject to change at any time."]
